  ITItemName: Frammento di costo
  ITDesc: "Fornisce una quantit\xE0 casuale di costo utilizzabile solo in questo
    combattimento, tra 10 e 15."
  DEItemName: Kosten-Splitter
  DEDesc: "Gew\xE4hrt eine zuf\xE4llige Menge kampfgebundener Kosten zwischen 10
    und 15."
  ESItemName: Fragmento de coste
  ESDesc: Concede una cantidad aleatoria de coste utilizable solo en este combate,
    entre 10 y 15.
  JAItemName: "\u30B3\u30B9\u30C8\u306E\u6B20\u7247"
  JADesc: "\u3053\u306E\u6226\u95D8\u3067\u306E\u307F\u4F7F\u7528\u53EF\u80FD\u306A\u30B3\u30B9\u30C8\u309210\u301C15\u306E\u7BC4\u56F2\u3067\u30E9\u30F3\u30C0\u30E0\u306B\u4ED8\u4E0E\u3057\u307E\u3059\u3002"
  PT_BRItemName: Fragmento de Custo
  PT_BRDesc: "Concede uma quantidade aleat\xF3ria de custo utiliz\xE1vel apenas nesta
    batalha, entre 10 e 15."
  RUItemName: "\u041E\u0441\u043A\u043E\u043B\u043E\u043A \u0441\u0442\u043E\u0438\u043C\u043E\u0441\u0442\u0438"
  RUDesc: "\u0414\u0430\u0451\u0442 \u0441\u043B\u0443\u0447\u0430\u0439\u043D\u043E\u0435
